Shirley: I really wished that I could've seen you with my own eyes, and not through a method like this...
... My child.
Shirley: The quill I left with professor Ceres has a seal on it. The moment you awaken your feather tribe abilities, the seal will break and reveal this message.

Elio: Why did you choose to appear in front of me now!
Why did you abandon me back then!
Shirley: The first thing I want to tell you is...

Elio: So she can't reply to my questions in real time?
Is this a pre-recorded message?
Shirley: My name is not Clio. That's a fake name I used during my undercover mission in Rune Academy.
Elio: Fake name? Undercover? What exactly are you...
Shirley: There are so many things I want to say to you...
Shirley: ... However, the most important thing I have to tell you is the identity of your father.
Shirley: The fact that you see this message means that I was unable to return to your side in the end.
Shirley: If that's the case, then your existence is a threat to your father...
Shirley: My child, you must conceal your identity forever. You must also avoid your father at all costs; you cannot let him find out about your existence.
Shirley: Your father, his name is...
